{"tid":430229,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港青年自認中國人 跌至3.1%新低","createTime":"2017-10-09T15:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T15:27:19.000Z","uid":28366,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bbabb447c7d5e79599f1604470872f6c3a9e0806","tid":430229,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T15:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jsx03w5t\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjsx03w5t&h=976542ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">過去5年不論北京還是港府均全力硬推愛國主義，惟港人對中國人身份認同未見上升，在年輕人當中更跌至谷底。（資料圖片）(蘋果日報)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/scv28bnr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fscv28bnr&h=d4238377&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國家主席習近平2012年十八大後開始掌權，也是特首梁振英5年任期開始。過去5年不論北京還是港府，均全力硬推愛國主義、打擊本土及港獨，但5年下來，港人對中國人身份認同並無上升，年輕人對中國人身份認同更是跌至谷底。<br />\n<br />\n港大民意研究計劃每半年調查港人身份認同。5年前習近平和梁振英分別成為中國和香港的第一把手時，自認為廣義上的中國人，意思是自認為中國人或香港的中國人中，30歲以下的年輕人有近14%。&nbsp;<br />\n高位達17.5%<br />\n<br />\n自2012年中起打後兩年，有關數介乎11%至15%之間，直到2014年下旬，即佔領運動尾聲之際，年輕人中國人身份認同升至17.5%的5年高位，一般相信與當時盛傳習叫停梁開槍對付示威者，部份年輕人未對北京太反感有關。<br />\n<br />\n可是自梁於2015年借發表施政報告狠批港大學生會刊物《學苑》，繼而掀起反港獨運動後，年輕人對中國認同感不斷下跌。 2015年6月調查，僅13%年輕人自認為中國人，一年後跌至8.5%，到今年6月再下挫至僅3.1%。與此同時，自認為廣義香港人，即表示自己是香港人或中國的香港人的年輕人，由梁振英上場後的85%，攀升至今年6月的93.7%。<br />\n<br />\n相對而言，30歲以上人士自認為廣義上中國人的比例，過去5年間都在33%至43%之間上落，而自認為廣義上香港人的比例，則在54%至64%之間徘徊。<br />\n<br />\n記者 呂浩然<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20171009&amp;guid=57306673&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20171009%26guid%3D57306673%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=9PqFEyek11r748RoE8T%2ByJzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=b1227f15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20171009%26guid%3D57306673%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=a64f24b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20171009&amp;guid=57306673&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"0bf483dabd13cb6413dd25473fd87d170d6a7a35","tid":430229,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T15:10:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60c14722df80cd453798e4daeb4d7078e6a5782","tid":430229,"uid":117032,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T15:17:26.000Z","msg":"連隻貓都蝦點撚認得落呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8867cc2e41e915ea645ffc91a503db540d1bad77","tid":430229,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T23:04:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連隻貓都蝦點撚認得落呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba1b3e76830510f75914b30eb4dfae30ec7d47d","tid":430229,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T23:06:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連隻貓都蝦點撚認得落呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係好冇人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc818d26cc99432e5b97d441fdb5bdb8aa4bcf0","tid":430229,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T12:34:31.000Z","msg":"認有咩問題？今日好多人慶祝國慶"},{"pid":"8a225e8e6791cb80d2ec54eada4b6d3e723ba041","tid":430229,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T12:38:44.000Z","msg":"又要斬樹又要殺貓又要覇公屋<br />\n邊個會認同支那人呀?<br />\n<br />\nbtw習總屋企人又係咩國籍呢？"},{"pid":"c39323437e22762bb7665ae01a177d79d9410ce6","tid":430229,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0